            <h3 class="mini-header">&gt; OBJECTIVES</h3>
            <ul class="objective-list">
              <li><span class="bullet">01</span> Overcome challenges for mining in homes and businesses</li>
              <li><span class="bullet">02</span> Spark partnerships that accelerate development</li>
              <li><span class="bullet">03</span> Network with hyper-focused builders</li>
